00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:47,224
iPad you know so I have like three devices on the go. What I did notice was that on my account

371
00:22:47,224 --> 00:22:49,186
because I've gone up to like level a thousand.

372
00:22:50,546 --> 00:22:53,868
I barely saw any ads or any intrusive anything.

373
00:22:53,868 --> 00:22:57,131
It was really easy to play and I was just continuously playing it.

374
00:22:57,131 --> 00:23:00,853
But when I played on my sister's phone or something,

375
00:23:00,853 --> 00:23:03,375
there would be ads popping up a bit more, you know.

376
00:23:03,375 --> 00:23:08,559
And to be honest, these kind of ads are a bit of a necessary evil,

377
00:23:08,559 --> 00:23:10,220
I guess, with free-to-play games.

378
00:23:10,220 --> 00:23:13,182
But the fact that they never show up on my account

379
00:23:13,182 --> 00:23:16,265
because I'm level 1000-something is kind of nice.

