00:27:54,624 --> 00:27:54,824
Yay!

456
00:28:02,949 --> 00:28:08,030
Probably you guys too, I mean that's my point. We're all gamers at heart and we're all game developers

457
00:28:08,030 --> 00:28:09,731
We do this because we love it

458
00:28:09,731 --> 00:28:14,073
And I'm pretty sure all of you remember your first games and you grew up thinking oh man

459
00:28:14,073 --> 00:28:19,034
I want to make that I want to make games that people enjoy and could remember by and

460
00:28:21,495 --> 00:28:24,335
I just want you to remember that when you go to work,

